5aa3bef4955edb7f1a20e2942f77daef413945ecd2cdd38699db213a8a0ca9b52c1e14df3b6a86dcfb870dc5f8862e988807892304bb4916a5105f9fcbe5a246  fix-null-pointer-dereference.patch"
